As a 40 druid, depending on the grouping location i do not hate earth pets. sometimes air is much better tho...depends on whos in group.<P>You have any idea what a couple druids grouped together can do in an outdoors zone? *cackle*<P>In a full group at high level best combo in my opinion: cleric (heal), warrior (shield), enchanter (mez/clarity)(a bard can take this spot, but prefer enchanter...both maybe), and then 2-3 others...at least one wizard or druid for porting/nuking purposes.
